Information update for the Finals November 4, 2023 @world_series_of_armwrestling

Less than 2 weeks to a packed finals! Remember that if you competed or were in the operations of the regionals you are qualified to compete! Would love to see the amateur classes as packed as the pro’s are right now!

Finishing up 1200 Sqft ADU just in time for clients to move in before Halloween. Oh yeah WSA finals November 4th!

Happy New Year everyone! I hope you are having an awesome day! WSA is same us, with 2 new faces in the New Year! We are super excited to announce Jamie Sheldon as our New Director of Athlete Relations! He will be working with our event hosts to communicate with teams inside and outside of the regions to assist, market, inform and listen to their concerns and needs! 

Also joining me in the Hosting Booth will be the Amazing and Super talented KD Aubert! KD will be taking the lead in developing our athlete stories for season 2 as well as beyond! KD is best known for Friday 2, Scorpion King, and Soul Plane… and of course Born 2 Hustle! We are excited to continue to develop our team with talented and amazing individuals!
Happy New Year! Follow @jodywilliams1976 and myself on YouTube and TikTok for our daily progress as we try to make it to 30! #pullupchallenge #armwrestler #happynewyear
